    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n5367" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλί̄νω</span></b> , aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔκλῑνα, κλῖναν</span>, pass. aor. (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐ</span>)<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλίνθη,
            ἐκλίθη</span>, perf. 3 pl. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κεκλίαται,
            κεκλιμένος</span>, plup. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κέκλιτο</span>,
          mid. aor. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κλῑνάμενος</span>: I. act.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">make to slope</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">incline, lean</span> one
          thing against another, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινί τι</span>, or
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πρός τι, Λ 593</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 22.121</span></i>; of turning away the eyes,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 3.427</span></i>; turning the tide of
          battle (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μάχην</span>, inclinare pugnam),
            <i><span class="en">Il. 14.510</span></i>, and esp. <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">put to
            flight</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 5.37</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od. 9.59</span></i>.—II. pass., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">bend oneself,
            sink</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">lie down;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐκλίνθη καὶ ἀλεύατο??ρα, ἑτέρωσ᾽ ἐκλίνθη κάρη,
            κλίνθη κεκμηώς,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 3.360</span></i>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc"> Ν
            543</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 23.232</span></i>;
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be supported, lean against</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινί, Λ 371</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 6.307</span></i>,
          mid., <i><span class="en">Od. 17.340</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
